# Postgre install from source

- Delete packages postgresql-lib postgresql postgresql-odbc

- Install packages:
  - readline-devel libxml2-devel libxslt-devel wget tmux bzip2 git gcc make flex bison jade

# See all flags ./configure --help
- Make from source
  - Make options
      --prefix=/opt/$PG_NAME
      --with-systemd
      --with_libxml
      --with_libxslt
      --with-openssl
      --with-ldap
      --with-pam
      # Add additional languages
      --with-perl
      --with-python
      --with-tcl

- Environment configuration

- Add Autovacuum jobs to Cron

- sysctl.conf config for postgres

- limits.conf config for postgres

- Additional software to use for administration
    - tmux
    - pgbouncer
    - pgcenter
    - pgBadger

 
